### ==========================================
### TRADING API - PUBLIC ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Get Ticker (BTC/USD - default)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/ticker

### Get Ticker (ETH/USD)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/ticker?symbol=ETH/USD

### Get Ticker (using Binance native symbol)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/ticker?symbol=BTCUSDT

### ==========================================
### TRADING API - PROTECTED ENDPOINTS (requires BINANCE_API_KEY & BINANCE_API_SECRET)
### ==========================================

### Get All Balances (non-zero only)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/balance

### Get BTC Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/balance/BTC

### Get USDT Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/balance/USDT

### Get ETH Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/trading/balance/ETH

